<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>定義：</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>由於冠狀動脈平滑肌的短暫血管痙攣（Vasospasm）所致，導致心肌缺血，變異性心絞痛並非由粥狀動脈硬化（Atherosclerosis）引起，但可能合併動脈粥樣硬化。常見於年輕吸菸者（&lt;50歲），但無明顯冠心病風險因素</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>診斷</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt' lang=3Den-US>主要依據病史（Clinical
     history）：</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:
      "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:black'>陣發性胸痛，常在</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>午夜至清晨</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:
      "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:black'>可能</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>休息時發作，運動後反而改善</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:
      "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:black'>典型症狀：</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#2E75B5'>壓迫感、悶痛，可輻射至手臂或下巴</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:5pt;
     margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
     font-size:16.0pt'>心電圖（ECG）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>ST
      段抬高（Transient ST Elevation）</span></li>
 </ul>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>發作間期
      ECG 可完全正常（silent ischemia）</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
     lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>冠狀動脈攝影（Coronary
     Angiography）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#2E75B5'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>冠狀動脈痙攣為診斷標誌（Diagnostic
      Hallmark）</span></li>
 </ul>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>約
      50% 患者合併動脈粥樣硬化斑塊</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
     lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>誘發試驗</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>過度換氣（Hyperventilation）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>冠狀動脈內注射乙醯膽鹼（Intracoronary
      Acetylcholine）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可誘發局部冠狀動脈狹窄或ST段抬高型心絞痛，確立診斷</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
     lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>治療</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>戒菸</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
      lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>藥物</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>鈣離子通道阻斷劑（Calcium
       Channel Blockers, CCB）</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>首選藥物，可擴張冠狀動脈、抑制血管痙攣</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>二氫吡啶類（Dihydropyridine CCB）：如 Amlodipine、Nifedipine</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>非二氫吡啶類（Non-dihydropyridine CCB）：如
        Verapamil、Diltiazem（適用於合併心律不整者）</span></li>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>硝酸鹽類（Nitrates）</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>急性發作時使用短效硝酸甘油（Nitroglycerin）</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>長效硝酸鹽（如 Isosorbide Mononitrate）可用於預防</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>禁忌藥物</span></li>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:
      "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>β-阻斷劑（Beta-blockers）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>特別是非選擇性
       β-blockers（如 Propranolol）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可能導致
       α 受體不受抑制，使血管痙攣加重</span></li>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:
      5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;color:black' lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:
      "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>阿司匹林（Aspirin）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
       lang=3Den-US><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可能抑制前列環素（Prostacyclin,
       PGI</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei Light";
       font-size:11.0pt'>₂</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>），導致血管收縮</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
</ul>

